item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row row_type="section" type="grid" bg_image_repeat="repeat" padding_bottom="70" css=".vc_custom_1410251098114{padding-top: 30px !important;}" parallax_speed="0.3" mute="muted"][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInLeft"][vc_column_text]Evolve comes with robust and inteligent Admin Panel. It allows for easy and intuitive to set all aspects of appearance and function of theme. Creating your own skin has never been as easy. Plenty of options allows you to create the unique appearance of the page with a few clicks without writing a single line of code. This quick guide to the built-in Evolve Custom Skin Creator will show you how to do it.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInRight"][vc_single_image border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" image="7174" img_size="full"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="section" type="grid" bg_image_repeat="repeat" padding_bottom="50" css=".vc_custom_1410251110456{padding-top: 70px !important;}" parallax_speed="0.3" mute="muted"][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInUp"][headline style="heading-line" subtitle="Subtitle text"]1. General Options and Layout[/headline][vc_column_text]Here you can set all general options of theme:
  • Theme width
  • Custom width for mobile devices
  • Sidebar width and position
  • Social icons positions

Navigation Settings[/headline][vc_column_text]Here you can set all general options of menu:
  • Menu depth
  • Animation type and speed for main menu
etc...[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInUp"][vc_single_image border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" image="7178" img_size="full"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="section" type="grid" bg_image_repeat="repeat" padding_bottom="50" css=".vc_custom_1410251134168{padding-top: 70px !important;}" parallax_speed="0.3" mute="muted"][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInUp"][headline style="heading-line" subtitle="Subtitle text"]3. Typography settings[/headline][vc_column_text]Here you can set fonts for theme. Evolve support:
  • Google fonts
  • Adobe Edge fonts
  • FontSquirel fonts (6 fonts pack delivered with theme)
You can use up to four different fonts paralel. In this section you can set default font size for headers and body.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInUp"][vc_single_image border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" image="7180" img_size="full"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="section" type="grid" bg_image_repeat="repeat" padding_bottom="50" css=".vc_custom_1410251144111{padding-top: 70px !important;}" parallax_speed="0.3" mute="muted"][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInUp"][headline style="heading-line" subtitle="Subtitle text"]4. Apperance settings[/headline][vc_column_text]Here is a really powerful skin creator. You can separatelly set all main graphic options for all page areas. You can choose from several custom controls as:
  • Color picker
  • Pattern picker
  • Image uploader
  • Opacity slider
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInUp"][vc_single_image border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" image="7182" img_size="full"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="section" type="grid" bg_image_repeat="repeat" padding_bottom="50" css=".vc_custom_1410251153295{padding-top: 70px !important;}" parallax_speed="0.3" mute="muted"][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInUp"][headline style="heading-line" subtitle="Subtitle text"]5. Content settings[/headline][vc_column_text]Here you can select some content related options as:

  • Display specific post metadata
  • Display author info
  • Default excerpt length
  • Default blog layout

Social API[/headline][vc_column_text]Here you can select some Social API related options as:

  • Use prefix free CSS
  • Use Captha in contact form
etc...[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInDown"][vc_single_image border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" image="7188" img_size="full"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="section" type="grid" bg_image_repeat="repeat" padding_bottom="50" css=".vc_custom_1410251184367{padding-top: 70px !important;}" parallax_speed="0.3" mute="muted"][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInDown"][headline style="heading-line" subtitle="Subtitle text"]8. Branding options settings[/headline][vc_column_text]Evolve theme and admin panel is fully rebrandable. Here you can set:
  • Logo for frontpage and admin admin panel
  • Text for copyright area
  • Favicon
etc...[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInDown"][vc_single_image border_color="grey" img_link_target="_self" image="7189" img_size="full"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="section" type="grid" bg_image_repeat="repeat" padding_bottom="50" css=".vc_custom_1410251193015{padding-top: 70px !important;}" parallax_speed="0.3" mute="muted"][vc_column width="1/2" dp_animation="fadeInDown"][headline style="heading-line" subtitle="Subtitle text"]9. SEO options settings[/headline][vc_column_text]Evolve have built-in support for advanced SEO options.
